of forced capitalism and scientific indoctrination. <br>
<br>
I would have all lawyers and used car salesmen sterilized (to prevent the contamination of future generations). I would abolish income taxes and replaces them with a sales tax. I would remove the governments of the world from doing anything that a private concern could do – relegating them to regulating (i.e., no government run ports, space programs, schools, etc). I would also abolish all taxes on property and inheritances. <br>
<br>
